      "comment": "FAST FREDDY (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (30.05) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and three minor placings from seven starts. Can discover winning form. IVORY INZAI (7) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when sixth at The Meadows over 525m behind Sparring (30.46) in a Grade 4/5. Key player if finds best. FLEEING (2) comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at Wentworth Park, scoring by 1.5 lengths (29.79). Capable of going close again. STOMPING (3) was below best last time at Ballarat (30.94) in a Special conditions race, finishing a 4 length fourth. Has already won four times from this draw.",
